STATE of North Carolina
v.
Arthur O. ARMSTRONG. No. 331P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Arthur O. Armstrong, Pro Se. Patricia A. Duffy, Assistant Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 20th day of June 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Wake County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
